# When creating/updating a Sub-Services section

- Use `useTranslation()` → `const { t } = useTranslation()`.
- For section header + CTA text, read from i18n keys (always provide `defaultValue`):
  - `serviceSections.<service>.subServices.sectionLabel`
  - `serviceSections.<service>.subServices.title`
  - `serviceSections.<service>.subServices.subtitle` (if used)
  - `serviceSections.<service>.subServices.description`
  - `serviceSections.<service>.subServices.learnMore`
- For cards (`items`), NEVER hardcode `title/desc`; map from:
  - `serviceSections.influencerMarketing.subServices.items`
  - `serviceSections.digitalMarketing.subServices.<group>`
  - (or use an existing helper like `getInfluencerMarketingSubServiceItems(t)` when present)
- Ensure `hrefs` and `icons` align by index with `items` (same ordering/length).
- For influencer marketing “related pages” lists, pass `t` into helpers (so titles/descriptions translate).
- Always pass `dir` from `isRtl ? "rtl" : "ltr"` and keep `classPrefix` consistent.

